---
const buses = [
  {
    origin: 'Kiosko de Rafa',
    departure: '--:-- h',
    return: '--:-- h',
  },
  {
    origin: 'El Comercial',
    departure: '--:-- h',
    return: '--:-- h',
  },
  {
    origin: 'Jerez',
    departure: '--:-- h',
    return: '--:-- h',
  },
];
---
<section id="autobuses" class="buses-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Autobuses</h2>
    <div class="section-divider reveal"><span>✦</span></div>

    <p class="buses-intro reveal">
      Para que podáis disfrutar sin preocupaciones, hemos organizado autobuses de ida y vuelta
      desde distintos puntos. Los horarios exactos os los confirmaremos próximamente.
    </p>

    <div class="buses-grid">
      {buses.map(b => (
        <div class="bus-card reveal">
          <div class="bus-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <rect x="4" y="8" width="28" height="18" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M4 14h28" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <line x1="16" y1="8" x2="16" y2="26" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3"/>
              <circle cx="10" cy="28" r="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none"/>
              <circle cx="26" cy="28" r="2.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M4 22h2M30 22h2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="bus-origin">{b.origin}</h3>
          <dl class="bus-info">
            <div class="bus-row">
              <dt>Salida</dt>
              <dd>{b.departure}</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="bus-row">
              <dt>Regreso</dt>
              <dd>{b.return}</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .buses-section {
    padding: var(--section-padding);
    background: var(--color-bg);
  }

  .buses-intro {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .buses-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.2rem;
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bus-card {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    text-align: center;
    transition: border-color 0.25s, box-shadow 0.25s;
  }

  .bus-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(184,147,106,0.1);
  }

  .bus-icon {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .bus-origin {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .bus-info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.45rem 1rem;
    width: fit-content;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .bus-row { display: contents; }

  .bus-row dt {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: right;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .bus-row dd {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    text-align: left;
  }

  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .buses-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 320px; margin-inline: auto; }
  }
</style>
